race.comment: AUTUMN GLOW (14) dominant four-year-old mare who faces her toughest test to date. Justified the short price when stalked the speed before asserting her class when an effortless winner of the G1 Epsom Handicap over 1600m at this track. Since fitted with a 1050m tick-over trial and can keep her unbeaten record intact. LINEBACKER (3) had the race parcelled up a long way out when a decisive winner of the G3 Silver Eagle over 1300m at this track. Proven Group 1 performer who can rattle the cage of AUTUMN GLOW. EVAPORATE (1) won the Carbine here in good style over the mile last April and comes here at his top. Unlucky when launched late for a narrow second over 1600m in the G1 Toorak Handicap at Caulfield. Rawiller rides and look for him to push forward. DEPTH OF CHARACTER (7) raced without luck all prep and is a much stronger chance than his current price suggests. Jason Collett sticks and look for him powering late. PERFUMIST (15) tough on-pace mare with excellent each way credentials.
